=================================================
Name: Simple Formatter
Version: 1.0.0
Requirements: Selenium IDE v1.0.8
=================================================

IMPORTANT:
This plugin is currently in alpha and not complete! It is recommended
that you do not build/install it unless you intend to work on it.

NOTE:
This is a plugin for Selenium IDE that adds a simple formatter, which can be
used to easily share examples of tests.

INSTALLATION:
1. Run build.bat (or build.sh on Linux).
2. Open simple-formatter.xpi in Firefox.

REQUIREMENTS:
To build on Windows you will need 7-Zip and Robocopy
* 7-Zip - http://www.7-zip.org/
* Robocopy - http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robocopy

